CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 20, 1962, pg. 1 reads: "Listening To Lambasting of the GOP by Kennedy were these persons, part of the many who attended the rally Friday at Pitt Field House."
TitMainTitle: Crowd of men and women, some holding signs inscribed "Support Kennedy vote Straight Democratic,"gathered in University of Pittsburgh Field House for President Kennedy visit
